1065.0   = G, Gravity [cm/s**2]
2.214    = FSCALE, stellar flux scaling (Seff); Earth=1.0
0.000    = ALB, Surface Albedo
0.0e+00  = ZTROP, height of the tropopause [cm]
0.000    = FAR, Ar partial pressure
6.99e+08 = R0, radius of planet [cm]
0.100    = P0, surface pressure [bar]
VENUS    = PLANET, string naming planet type
0.00    = TIMEGA, for modifying solar flux (SUN ONLY)
0        = IRESET
33       = MSUN
0        = IHZSCALE (set to 1 for SED-dep scaling)
4.95e+04 = DZGRID [cm]








